<!-- Definition and medical uses -->
'''柠檬酸咖啡因'''，商品名有'''Cafcit'''等，是一种用于治疗{{tsl|en|apnea of prematurity|早产儿呼吸暂停}}的药物。<ref name=AHFS2016/>一旦排除其他可能病因，这种药物就可用于治疗出生时不足35周龄，或体重不足2 kg的婴儿。<ref name=WHO2008>{{cite book|title=WHO Model Formulary 2008|date=2009|publisher=World Health Organization|isbn=9789241547659|page=X|url=http://apps.who.int/medicinedocs/documents/s16879e/s16879e.pdf|accessdate=8 December 2016|archive-date=2016-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213060118/http://apps.who.int/medicinedocs/documents/s16879e/s16879e.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>此药可通过口服或[[靜脈注射|慢速静滴]]给药。<ref name=AHFS2016>{{cite web|title=Caffeine; Caffeine and Sodium Benzoate Injection; Caffeine Citrate|url=https://www.drugs.com/monograph/caffeine-caffeine-and-sodium-benzoate-injection-caffeine-citrate.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|accessdate=8 December 2016|archive-date=2017-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716044142/https://www.drugs.com/monograph/caffeine-caffeine-and-sodium-benzoate-injection-caffeine-citrate.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
柠檬酸咖啡因可能造成喂食困难、心率上升、[[低血糖|低血糖]]、[[坏死性小肠结肠炎|坏死性小肠结肠炎]]、[[腎功能衰竭|腎功能衰竭]]等副作用，<ref name=WHO2008/><ref name=AHFS2016/>因而建议在给药时经常测量血中[[咖啡因|咖啡因]]浓度。<ref name=AHFS2016/>作为咖啡因的[[檸檬酸|檸檬酸]]盐，<ref>{{cite book|last1=Donn|first1=Steven M.|last2=Sinha|first2=Sunil K.|title=Manual of Neonatal Respiratory Care|date=2012|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=9781461421559|page=457|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=9rnVSufZFFwC&pg=PA457|language=en|access-date=2017-01-29|archive-date=2016-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230000058/https://books.google.ca/books?id=9rnVSufZFFwC&pg=PA457|dead-url=no}}</ref>本药属[[黄嘌呤|黄嘌呤]]类药物。<ref name=WHO2008/>其兴奋作用可以刺激[[脑|脑]]中的{{tsl|en|respiratory centers|呼吸中枢}}。<ref name=AHFS2016/>

<!-- History and culture -->
咖啡因于1819年发现。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Brown|first1=Nathan|title=In Silico Medicinal Chemistry: Computational Methods to Support Drug Design|date=2015|publisher=Royal Society of Chemistry|isbn=9781782621638|page=20|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=kLfbCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA20|language=en|access-date=2017-01-29|archive-date=2016-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229171147/https://books.google.ca/books?id=kLfbCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA20|dead-url=no}}</ref>柠檬酸咖啡因列于[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]，是[[醫療系統|醫療系統]]中最重要的药品之一。<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO Model List of Essential Medicines|url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=22 April 2014|date=October 2013|archive-date=2014-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423005004/http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>在英国，每小瓶10 mg药物售价约4.90英镑。<!-- <ref name=Ai2014/> -->用于静滴的包装也可经口服用。<ref name=Ai2014>{{cite book|last1=Ainsworth|first1=Sean B.|title=Neonatal Formulary: Drug Use in Pregnancy and the First Year of Life|date=2014|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9781118819517|page=120|edition=7|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=EORvBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA120|language=en|access-date=2017-01-29|archive-date=2016-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230002108/https://books.google.ca/books?id=EORvBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA120|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==製備==
柠檬酸咖啡因可由{{le|無水|Anhydrous}}咖啡因和[[柠檬酸|柠檬酸]]一水合物及[[檸檬酸鈉|檸檬酸鈉]]二水合物混合得到。

